{{DISPLAYTITLE:Pillar_BuildAndCrush}} {{Special|94|tag, speed, height, crush [,crushmode]|Floor and Ceiling}}
* ''tag'': Tag of affected sector * ''speed'': Speed of the build * ''height'': Height (relative to floor) where the floor and ceiling meet * ''crush'': Amount of damage to apply * ''crushmode'': Sets the [[crushing mode]]
This is the same as [[Pillar_Build]] except that it will also apply crushing damage to anything blocking the pillar from closing.
